 Experience in managing information resources, applying information tools and technologies. For more information and to apply online by May 15th, 2024, please go to: https://bcpublicservice.hua.hrsmart.com/hr/ats/Posting/view/111643 Compensation $41.65 to $47.45 hourly Closes: 15 May, 2024 Ministry of Health Victoria , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
